00:00:01.880 --> 00:00:06.000
EGGPLANT SALAD

00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:09.619
I am pleased to welcome you in the kitchen!

00:00:09.619 --> 00:00:13.839
Today's guest of our kitchen - an eggplant!

00:00:13.839 --> 00:00:18.599
We will prepare very interesting and tasty salad with eggplants.

00:00:18.599 --> 00:00:23.300
Take fresh eggplants, plucked from the garden.

00:00:23.300 --> 00:00:27.380
Cut off their stems.

00:00:27.380 --> 00:00:29.509
We do not need it.

00:00:29.509 --> 00:00:36.509
Remove peel.

00:00:37.600 --> 00:00:40.250
A thin layer.

00:00:40.250 --> 00:00:47.580
While frying peel becomes hard and can spoil all the dish.

00:00:47.580 --> 00:00:51.500
It is better to remove it.

00:00:53.530 --> 00:00:58.000
Cut eggplant into rings.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:03.300
5 mm thick.

00:01:09.270 --> 00:01:15.200
Now cut into strips.

00:01:25.480 --> 00:01:30.710
Shift the eggplants into strainer.

00:01:30.710 --> 00:01:33.100
Such dishes with holes.

00:01:33.100 --> 00:01:37.500
Sprinkle eggplant with salt.

00:01:37.500 --> 00:01:43.400
Leave for 30 minutes, to bitterness left together with the juice.

00:01:46.780 --> 00:01:48.790
Now marinate the onions.

00:01:48.790 --> 00:01:51.480
Take a small onion.

00:01:51.480 --> 00:01:58.390
Cut it in half and cut into half rings.

00:01:58.390 --> 00:02:05.390
Thin, neat semicircles.

00:02:21.779 --> 00:02:27.100
Shift the semicircles in a bowl.

00:02:32.900 --> 00:02:39.700
Here add 1 tablespoon of sugar.

00:02:40.900 --> 00:02:45.954
Vinegar.

00:02:45.989 --> 00:02:50.809
Two tablespoons.

00:02:52.649 --> 00:02:57.889
Add boiling water.

00:02:57.889 --> 00:03:00.799
Water covered everything.

00:03:00.799 --> 00:03:04.500
Give it to brew for 15-20 minutes.

00:03:05.379 --> 00:03:07.609
The eggplants have given juice.

00:03:07.609 --> 00:03:14.909
Clean with a towel the remaining juice on eggplants.

00:03:14.909 --> 00:03:17.899
Lightly crush.

00:03:17.899 --> 00:03:25.100
Will prepare fried eggplant.

00:03:25.100 --> 00:03:32.499
We are putting them in a hot vegetable oil.

00:03:32.499 --> 00:03:36.761
Fry till golden brown.

00:03:36.761 --> 00:03:39.900
Cooking like French fries.

00:03:42.130 --> 00:03:47.279
Begin to make up an eggplant salad.

00:03:47.279 --> 00:03:56.469
Put down fried eggplants.

00:03:56.469 --> 00:04:02.869
Now there is a layer of pickled onions.

00:04:02.869 --> 00:04:09.249
Put much onions.

00:04:10.389 --> 00:04:14.379
Egg.

00:04:16.379 --> 00:04:23.600
Cut egg slices or half rings.

00:04:30.870 --> 00:04:37.189
Add a sprig of dill.

00:04:37.189 --> 00:04:43.700
Top - a little eggplants.

00:04:43.700 --> 00:04:48.289
Tasting.

00:04:48.289 --> 00:04:55.289
Cut tomatoes.

00:05:03.680 --> 00:05:10.680
Homemade mayonnaise - 1 spoon.

00:05:10.680 --> 00:05:13.219
Thats all - salad is ready!

00:05:13.219 --> 00:05:17.900
Enjoy all the meal!

